{"tid":1204222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中］一個人 亂諗嘢亂寫字 藝術嘢","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:26.000Z","uid":76829,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5d67af5408901e456c415a7337efa77f397d90","tid":1204222,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"6月12，會發生咩事冇人知<br />\n我會出嚟，但係我驚，好驚，驚好多嘢<br />\n驚走唔切、驚受傷、驚殘廢、驚警棍、驚胡椒噴霧、驚催淚彈、驚橡膠子彈、驚音波炮... <br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得點都唔夠通過到修訂逃犯條例驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔會比自己後悔<br />\n萬一條例過咗，我寧願有做過嘢比人移交返大陸<br />\n都好過咩都冇做過，然後比人移交<br />\n<br />\n遊行，我行左<br />\n聽日，我會野餐<br />\n<br />\n我只想保護同守住我屋企，香港<br />\n我比較擅長嘅只係寫字，係我可以做到嘅嘢...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTADz6i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTADz6i.png&h=54a210a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9ppvEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9ppvEE.png&h=a03ee19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MXuGMm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MXuGMm.png&h=490c7771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTsB6c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTsB6c2.png&h=ead9674a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n守護家同Say No to China Extradition張底圖係我自己影架<br />\n啲字同相未必係你心水，我只係想通過某啲嘢嚟表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01b0a3ec39d0d33fa4c4a55bd0e66826acfa0cc","tid":1204222,"uid":224961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5d67af5408901e456c415a7337efa77f397d90","tid":1204222,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"6月12，會發生咩事冇人知<br />\n我會出嚟，但係我驚，好驚，驚好多嘢<br />\n驚走唔切、驚受傷、驚殘廢、驚警棍、驚胡椒噴霧、驚催淚彈、驚橡膠子彈、驚音波炮... <br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得點都唔夠通過到修訂逃犯條例驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill